Day 37 — Ridge Regression

 Overview

On Day 37, I learned Ridge Regression, a Regularization technique used to reduce overfitting in Linear Regression.

 What is Ridge Regression?

Ridge Regression adds a penalty term to the cost function to control large coefficients.

 Formula

Loss = RSS + \lambda \sum w^2

λ (Lambda) → Regularization parameter

Penalizes large weights

Helps reduce overfitting
